Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hello mexite What we are essentially offering is a platform to bring both users and service providers together to take care of supply and demand in a safe environment for everyone. It’s about connecting those who want something done to someone who can get that job done regardless of the complexity or simplicity of it. Since GIG9 will be based on blockchain technology powered by smart contracts, security, organisation, transparency, viability and connectivity will never be an issue.  GIG9 will basically create the fairest, and the most transparent and efficient service marketplace. And this will also be beneficial to companies looking for freelancers for work and vice versa. There’s nothing like trust especially when it comes to quality and payment. GIG9’s technology ensures all parties of this!  GIG9 will charge as minimum as 1% for using our service. This industry-leading service fee will be the foundation for our worldwide popularity as this further showcases the usability for anyone in the world.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hi,  Thank you very much for showing your interest in our token. 9Coin is based on QTM economics model of money. In simple words, it is a utility token integrated to use on the platform in exchange of services. How? With benefits, discounts and generous rewards, the platform encourages the users to adopt tokens,  the network grows the value of token increases with the increase in demand, given the limited number of supply of the tokens.  So, the token value is based on real services exchanged by real people in 2 Trillion dollars worth economy. Additionally, the liquidity is ensured as 9coin is convertible to other cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, LTC and even fiat! The good news for contributors is this would lead to a huge price increase of a token resulting in a profit for early token holders. The thing every investor should look for is a strong reason why token demand should increase over time. Please read our financial valuation report at https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gig9/gig9_marketReport.pdf and watch https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mF33-_9Sy3E to learn more about a revolutionary token model.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hello ainimarch112 GIG9 was founded by an exceptionally successful group of Oxford Fintech Program members whose passion to change the face of our global economy came to life through their tireless efforts. After laying down the foundation for the idea, they embraced the task of individually selecting the best minds around the globe to form a team who would bring this idea to reality through research, financial advisory, technical expertise, marketing strategies and overall business development.  With a combined experience of about 250 years in the service industry and beyond spanning over 14 nationalities and 27 languages, we have discovered the formula to disrupting the global economy as we know it.

Author: ainimarch112
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: What is the unique selling proposition of GIG9 in comparison with other initiatives in the direction of freelance communities?

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: We have found our niche in establishing a direct connection between users and local service providers. Current freelancing platforms such as Upwork, Freelance and Fiverr focus on businesses and independent professionals connecting and collaborating remotely. What GIG9 does is provide a personal touch and allow users to get the job done locally with over 150 different types of service providers within their vicinity be it plumbers, electricians, handymen, photographers, nannies, lawyers and so much more.  Similar to Uber, we operate on a “Provider Navigation System” where users have the ability to actively track the location of their service provider on a map due to our enhanced GPS-mapping technology. This eliminates problems of unwanted delays and irritable time schedules allowing both users and providers to track and plan their schedules accordingly.  Additionally, our users can enjoy the benefits of not having to pay any advertising costs, sign up costs or membership fees. They can simply download our easy-to-use app and sign up to an advantageous experience of real reviews, secure transactions and fair pricing since GIG9 is a decentralised peer-to-peer marketplace built on blockchain technology.  Also, GIG9 will provide an escrow service powered by smart contracts to ensure that all parties are protected in a transaction.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Thanks Twinkledoe It engulfs anyone with a smartphone and a skill or merely a lending hand who either needs something done or who’s willing and ready to get the job done. It’s estimated that 5 billion people will have smartphones by 2019. So, we’re looking at taking advantage of the entire $2 trillion sharing economy that GIG9 aims to disrupt.  We are also in talks with different governments around the world to ensure this platform is accepted and adopted to see our mission through. Our MVP will be launched very soon and we shall be using the next 6 months to ensure we have an ample database for our product launch in early 2019.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: GIG9 is a peer-to-peer decentralized self-regulated international ecosystem, directly connecting local service providers and users, powered by blockchain-based smart contracts.GIG9 is an incredible app that connects people who need service (users) to local providers of services (providers) simply by a single tap of your smartphone whilst empowering you with honest reviews, flexible payments, and the ability to watch your provider heading towards your door on the map using GPS mapping technology. Additionally, GIG9 will provide an escrow service powered by smart contracts to ensure that all parties are protected in a transaction. GIG9 is an end-to-end solution providing discovery, engagement, job tracking, payment, receipt issuance and review capture. Our users can also avail to amazing features such as chatbot messaging, free voice calling, free invoicing and free quotation service.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: To solve major problems in this industry such as "Lack of Real Identity", "Lack of Real Performance Metrics", "Lack of User Knowledge", "Lack of Efficiency and Trade Semplicity".  We plan to solve all these issues by providing:  1) Identity verification through the utilization of blockchain technology and a decentralized network to establish trust and transparency between parties.  2) Providing an intelligent system leveraging both blockchain technology and artificial intelligenceto assess performance. Furthermore, GIG9 will provide affordable enterprise tools to measure, track and accomplish tasks.  3) Providing an easy to use leveraged knowledge bank from the system which simplifies the user experiences on a given task.  4) Deploying both a stable cryptocurrency to ease and simplify trade and "smart contracts" as payment terminations.  I'd invite you to read our Whitepaper to know more about our project.  Page 28 to 30 to read more about your question.   LINK to WhitePaper: https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gig9/May5_Whitepaper+(1).pdf

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: GIG9 is Freelance Local services ecosystem. I am sure that there's a lot of promising platforms. GIG9 is not just a promising platform. GIG9 is a peer-to-peer decentralized self-regulated ecosystem, directly connecting local service providers and users, powered by blockchain-based smart contracts. We will connect people who need services (users) to the local providers of services (providers) simply by using our smartphones, whilst be empowering honest reviews, flexible payments, and the ability to watch the provider heading towards our door on the map using GPS mapping technology. Additionally, GIG9 will provide an escrow service powered by smart contracts to ensure that all parties are protected in a transaction. It is an end-to-end solution providing discovery, engagement, job tracking, payment, receipt issuance and review capture

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Thank you for your questions.   GIG9 is a Decentralized Self-Regulated Freelance Ecosystem, Directly Connecting Local Service Providers and Consumers, Powered by Blockchain-Based Smart Contracts The GIG9’s platform will be the first of its kind to promote a peer-to-peer decentralized marketplace, controlled independently by the market participants.  Please, visit: https://www.gig9.io/

Body: Here's a link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=98IK1qFleWQ - it's a video so you can have some visual aids as well.  Of course, there are some points there that are similar to other freelance platforms.  What truly makes GIG9 stand out: - The fact that we focus on local service providers. We have the whole "empowering local communities" and "focusing on the heart of the economy" thing going on. - That bring us to our GEO-mapping technology which kinda makes us like the Uber of freelance services. You can track the location of your providers on a map. - We are heavy in our CSR. Equal opportunities for everyone irrespective of age, gender, background or physical ability. Which sure, is present in other platforms, but we actually speak about them - women empowerment, older skilled workers, young business leaders and workers with disabilities. - We also have Women in Blockchain UK which we will use as a partner for GIG9 to help encourage and empower women.  Also, another thing is the GIG9 token - 9Coin whose value will increase according to the number of jobs completed. So, the liquidity is there due to the fact that it is backed by real services.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hi Ameliajon3636  Thank you very much for showing your interest in our token. 9Coin is based on QTM economics model of money. In simple words, it is a utility token integrated to use on the platform in exchange for services. How? With benefits, discounts and generous rewards, the platform encourages the users to adopt tokens,  the network grows the value of token increases with the increase in demand, given the limited number of supply of the tokens.  So, the token value is based on real services exchanged by real people in 2 Trillion dollars worth economy. Additionally, the liquidity is ensured as 9coin is convertible to other cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, LTC and even fiat! The good news for contributors is this would lead to a huge price increase of a token resulting in a profit for early token holders. The thing every investor should look for is a strong reason why token demand should increase over time. Please read our financial valuation report at https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gig9/gig9_marketReport.pdf and watch https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mF33-_9Sy3E to learn more about the revolutionary token model.[/size]

Author: gig9_staff
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: We have found our niche in establishing a direct connection between users and local service providers. Current freelancing platforms such as Upwork, Freelance and Fiverr focus on businesses and independent professionals connecting and collaborating remotely. What GIG9 does is provide a personal touch and allow users to get the job done locally with over 150 different types of service providers within their vicinity be it plumbers, electricians, handymen, photographers, nannies, lawyers and so much more.  Similar to Uber, we operate on a “Provider Navigation System” where users have the ability to actively track the location of their service provider on a map due to our enhanced GPS-mapping technology. This eliminates problems of unwanted delays and irritable time schedules allowing both users and providers to track and plan their schedules accordingly.  Additionally, our users can enjoy the benefits of not having to pay any advertising costs, sign up costs or membership fees. They can simply download our easy-to-use app and sign up to an advantageous experience of real reviews, secure transactions and fair pricing since GIG9 is a decentralised peer-to-peer marketplace built on blockchain technology.  Also, GIG9 will provide an escrow service powered by smart contracts to ensure that all parties are protected in a transaction.

Author: gig9_staff
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Thank you for your question.  The purpose of the blockchain technology in GIG9 project is to leverage a range of solutions from in-house to cloud and service provider data centers to closely knit the multiple level of APIs, mapping services, temporary and permanent data storage needs as well as end users or business applications integrations. It shall also provide an easy-to-use frontend interface. The analytical, reporting and monitoring engines, provide a range of data streams, which will strengthen the AI component for a speedy, transparent and verified provisioning of any service. GIG9 will support multiple blockchains for scalability and performance. A smart contract shall facilitate a transparent exchange of service and currency. All this will be achieved by using well-known technologies such as Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, Real-time Analytics etc. used by successful companies such as Google, Microsoft and Uber.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hello thedarkk,  Here's a link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=98IK1qFleWQ - it's a video so you can have some visual aids as well.  Of course, there are some points there that are similar to other freelance platforms.  What truly makes GIG9 stand out: - The fact that we focus on local service providers. We have the whole "empowering local communities" and "focusing on the heart of the economy" thing going on. - That bring us to our GEO-mapping technology which kinda makes us like the Uber of freelance services. You can track the location of your providers on a map. - We are heavy in our CSR. Equal opportunities for everyone irrespective of age, gender, background or physical ability. Which sure, is present in other platforms, but we actually speak about them - women empowerment, older skilled workers, young business leaders and workers with disabilities. - We also have Women in Blockchain UK which we will use as a partner for GIG9 to help encourage and empower women.  Also, another thing is the GIG9 token - 9Coin whose value will increase according to the number of jobs completed. So, the liquidity is there due to the fact that it is backed by real services.  Cris

Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: To solve major problems in this industry such as "Lack of Real Identity", "Lack of Real Performance Metrics", "Lack of User Knowledge", "Lack of Efficiency and Trade Semplicity".  We plan to solve all these issues by providing:  1) Identity verification through the utilization of blockchain technology and a decentralized network to establish trust and transparency between parties.  2) Providing an intelligent system leveraging both blockchain technology and artificial intelligenceto assess performance. Furthermore, GIG9 will provide affordable enterprise tools to measure, track and accomplish tasks.  3) Providing an easy to use leveraged knowledge bank from the system which simplifies the user experiences on a given task.  4) Deploying both a stable cryptocurrency to ease and simplify trade and "smart contracts" as payment terminations.  I'd invite you to read our Whitepaper to know more about our project.  Page 28 to 30 to read more about your question.   LINK to WhitePaper: https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gig9/May5_Whitepaper+(1).pdf

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Quote from: kwakufavour on April 29, 2018, 11:55:41 PM There are so much about Freelance in the cryptospace these days. I dunno what makes this one special from the rest. Adding additional advantage of Gig9 over the other Freelance services will encourage potential invest. Are there any talks with exchanges to list soon after ico   Hello Nikka and kwakufavour!  Here's a link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=98IK1qFleWQ - it's a video so you can have some visual aids as well.  Of course, there are some points there that are similar to other freelance platforms.  What truly makes GIG9 stand out: - The fact that we focus on local service providers. We have the whole "empowering local communities" and "focusing on the heart of the economy" thing going on. - That bring us to our GEO-mapping technology which kinda makes us like the Uber of freelance services. You can track the location of your providers on a map. - We are heavy in our CSR. Equal opportunities for everyone irrespective of age, gender, background or physical ability. Which sure, is present in other platforms, but we actually speak about them - women empowerment, older skilled workers, young business leaders and workers with disabilities. - We also have Women in Blockchain UK which we will use as a partner for GIG9 to help encourage and empower women.  Also, another thing is the GIG9 token - 9Coin whose value will increase according to the number of jobs completed. So, the liquidity is there due to the fact that it is backed by real services.  Cris

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hi pauljen367 Thank you for your question.  The purpose of the blockchain technology in GIG9 project is to leverage a range of solutions from in-house to cloud and service provider data centers to closely knit the multiple level of APIs, mapping services, temporary and permanent data storage needs as well as end users or business applications integrations. It shall also provide an easy-to-use frontend interface. The analytical, reporting and monitoring engines, provide a range of data streams, which will strengthen the AI component for a speedy, transparent and verified provisioning of any service. GIG9 will support multiple blockchains for scalability and performance. A smart contract shall facilitate a transparent exchange of service and currency. All this will be achieved by using well-known technologies such as Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, Real-time Analytics etc. used by successful companies such as Google, Microsoft and Uber.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hi Ameliajon3636  Thank you very much for showing your interest in our token. 9Coin is based on QTM economics model of money. In simple words, it is a utility token integrated to use on the platform in exchange for services. How? With benefits, discounts and generous rewards, the platform encourages the users to adopt tokens,  the network grows the value of token increases with the increase in demand, given the limited number of supply of the tokens.  So, the token value is based on real services exchanged by real people in 2 Trillion dollars worth economy. Additionally, the liquidity is ensured as 9coin is convertible to other cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, LTC and even fiat! The good news for contributors is this would lead to a huge price increase of a token resulting in a profit for early token holders. The thing every investor should look for is a strong reason why token demand should increase over time. Please read our financial valuation report at https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gig9/gig9_marketReport.pdf and watch https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mF33-_9Sy3E to learn more about the revolutionary token model.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hi,  Thank you very much for showing your interest in our token. 9Coin is based on QTM economics model of money. In simple words, it is a utility token integrated to use on the platform in exchange of services. How? With benefits, discounts and generous rewards, the platform encourages the users to adopt tokens,  the network grows the value of token increases with the increase in demand, given the limited number of supply of the tokens.  So, the token value is based on real services exchanged by real people in 2 Trillion dollars worth economy. Additionally, the liquidity is ensured as 9coin is convertible to other cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, LTC and even fiat! The good news for contributors is this would lead to a huge price increase of a token resulting in a profit for early token holders. The thing every investor should look for is a strong reason why token demand should increase over time. Please read our financial valuation report at https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gig9/gig9_marketReport.pdf and watch https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mF33-_9Sy3E to learn more about a revolutionary token model.

Author: GIG9BTForum
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GIG9 – A Freelance Ecosystem Powered by Blockchain.
Body: Hi ILUzbek,  GIG9 is Freelance Local services ecosystem. I am sure that there's a lot of promising platforms. GIG9 is not just a promising platform. GIG9 is a peer-to-peer decentralized self-regulated ecosystem, directly connecting local service providers and users, powered by blockchain-based smart contracts. We will connect people who need services (users) to the local providers of services (providers) simply by using our smartphones, whilst be empowering honest reviews, flexible payments, and the ability to watch the provider heading towards our door on the map using GPS mapping technology. Additionally, GIG9 will provide an escrow service powered by smart contracts to ensure that all parties are protected in a transaction. It is an end-to-end solution providing discovery, engagement, job tracking, payment, receipt issuance and review capture.
